import React from "react"

function Input() {
    return (
        <form id="todo">
            <label for="input">Todo: </label>
            <input
            type="text"
            id="input"
            name="input" 
            placeholder='Enter your input here' 
            />
            <button type="button" form='todo'>Submit</button>
        </form>
    )
}

export default Input
